{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2043068, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 398764, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "硬盘空间得512G+，血泪教训", "timestamp": 1625987813, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2043177, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 398764, "reply_to": 2043068, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 为啥", "timestamp": 1625988677, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2043487, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 398764, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "建议独立显卡，预算充足就选好显卡", "timestamp": 1625991454, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2043527, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 398764, "reply_to": 2043177, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 要用到很多软件，包括不限于AutoCAD，SolidWorks，Multisim，QuartusII，MATLAB，Microsoft Visual Studio，pycharm，此外需要安装完整的c++架构，Java架构，Python及其各种拓展包/anaconda，此外需要大量的存储保存你的作业和资料", "timestamp": 1625991681, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2043538, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 398764, "reply_to": 2043177, "tag": null, "text": "我的推荐是拯救者新款，CPU i7起步，显卡建议3060往上（3050ti也不是不行，总之是个游戏本的独显，3050以上级别就算能用）。代价就是比较笨重", "timestamp": 1625991780, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2043541, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 398764, "reply_to": 2043177, "tag": null, "text": "等到跑机器学习的时候，就可以用自己的电脑跑一些小case", "timestamp": 1625991814, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2044023, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 398764, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "512G已经不能存游戏了", "timestamp": 1625996425, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2044033, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 398764, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "抱歉不是很赞同Carol的话，CPU和硬盘大一些就够了，显卡倒没必要，后期需要跑深度学习时借用实验室服务器就行，没必要前期就花大价钱买优质独显。至于AutoCAD SolidWorks，都是用完就卸，Multisim QuartusII也是大二结束就卸载，VS Pycharm等见仁见智，我都是VS Code+走天下。", "timestamp": 1625996502, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2044050, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 398764, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "cz配置：某轻薄本 + CPU i5 + 8GB + 512GB + 集显，特别舒服没遇到什么算力瓶颈。到了大三下推研确定后，anaconda env迁移到服务器上，需要时直接ssh + 端口映射就好，自己的笔记本更是完全不承担任何中大型计算", "timestamp": 1625996662, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2044651, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 398764, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "太感谢大家了！", "timestamp": 1626002731, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 11, "pid": 398764, "reply": 10, "tag": null, "text": "自动化方向有没有什么电脑推荐？", "timestamp": 1625987702, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1626002731, "url": "", "vote": {}}}